[b]2.3 - Step 3 - Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1.java(Sprites)[/b]
Now for the sprite part. Which most people don't do right.
Open up Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1.java and replace all:
[QUOTE]./Sprites/[/QUOTE]
with this
<blockquote>C:/.yourclientname_file_store_32/Sprites/</blockquote>
Like this:
[IMG]http://img5.imageshack.us/img5/5042/likethisr.png[/img]
[b]Also[/b] Replace:
[QUOTE]./Lunar/[/QUOTE] (If Lunar is a folder in your flient files do this)
with this
<blockquote>C:/.yourclientname_file_store_32/Sprites/</blockquote>
Do the same for the background
In Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1.java search for 
[QUOTE]
./
[/QUOTE]
If anything comes up that does not have a C:/ infront of it, delete the . and add this in front of it
<blockquote>C:/.yourclientname_file_store_32/</blockquote>

Once you have changed the location your client reads the sprites from your gonna wanna save the file and close it.

